%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'stepAfter', 'nodeSpacing': 30, 'rankSpacing': 40}}}%%
flowchart LR
    classDef startEnd fill:#000,stroke:#000,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B,color:#000
    classDef activity fill:#fff,stroke:#000,color:#000

    Start((Start)):::startEnd

    Start --> UserValid[User<br/>Validation]:::activity
    UserValid --> AuthCheck{Login<br/>Failed}:::decision
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| ForgotPW[Forgot Password]:::activity
    ForgotPW --> ResetPW[Reset<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetPW --> UserValid
    AuthCheck -->|No| Dashboard[Display Team<br/>Management<br/>Dashboard]:::activity
    Dashboard --> D1{Action?}:::decision

    D1 -->|Logout| Logout[Log out]:::activity
    Logout --> EndL((End)):::startEnd

    D1 -->|Invite User| EnterEmail[Enter User<br/>Email Address]:::activity
    EnterEmail --> CreateMember[Create Environment<br/>Membership]:::activity
    CreateMember --> InviteOK[User Added to<br/>Team Members]:::activity
    InviteOK --> MA{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|Remove User| SelectMember[Select Team<br/>Member]:::activity
    SelectMember --> ConfirmRemove{Confirm<br/>removal?}:::decision
    ConfirmRemove -->|Yes| DeleteMember[Delete Environment<br/>Membership]:::activity
    DeleteMember --> MB{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    ConfirmRemove -->|No| MB

    D1 -->|Reset Invite| RegenInvite[Regenerate<br/>Invite Code<br/>& PIN]:::activity
    RegenInvite --> DisplayCode[Display New<br/>Invite Credentials]:::activity
    DisplayCode --> MC{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|Manage Subscription| SelectPlan[Select New<br/>Team Plan]:::activity
    SelectPlan --> Payment[Process Stripe<br/>Payment]:::activity
    Payment --> MigrateTeam[Migrate All<br/>Members to<br/>New Tier DB]:::activity
    MigrateTeam --> MD{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    MA -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MB -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MC -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MD -->|Yes| Dashboard

    MA -->|No| E1((End)):::startEnd
    MB -->|No| E2((End)):::startEnd
    MC -->|No| E3((End)):::startEnd
    MD -->|No| E4((End)):::startEnd
